title: 3 bdrs Luxury Renovated 2nd floor floor
posting_body: ['Great BEAUTIFUL 3 Bdrs Apt.', 'Location, Location Location', 'Frog Hollow is a predominantly residential community minutes from Downtown Hartford and Trinity College.', 'The entire neighborhood is listed on the National Register of Historic Places and covers more than 150 acres.', 'Between 1850 and 1930, Frog Hollow experienced a rapid increase in development – many of these buildings and homes still stand today.', 'The name of the community was taken from the marsh lands near the intersection of Broad and Ward Streets.', 'Residents adore its international fare restaurants along Park Street.', 'Firebox is a gourmet restaurant in town with an impressive menu, and it’s in walking distance of Columbus Green park and Bushnell theater.', 'Located at the hart of Frog Hollow close to restaurants, farm market and main roads.', 'only a few blocks from Hartford Hospital and the CT Children Medical Center.', '* Luxury fully renovated, everything new.', '* Direct Entrance from the back parking lot.', '* 3 BDRS 1 Bath', '* 2 Balconies with the Capitol building view.', '* 6 building units.', '* Stainless steel appliances including Micro and Dishwasher.', '*  Open concept with Quartz HUGE countertop', '* Stainless steel appliances including Fridge, Stove, Micro, and Dishwasher', '*  Washer /Dryer in the laundry room in the unit.', '* Close to downtown, main roads, Hospitals, across the street of restaurants, and much more....', '* Cold flat- tenant is paying electric and gas.', 'Our company works on a first-come, first-serve basis.', 'We will place an apartment on hold and no longer perform showings once a security deposit is placed on the unit.', 'Income verification no vouchers or any program.', 'Please no dogs of any kind.', 'Cats welcome.', 'Please contact Roni the owner at', 'show contact info', 'to get more info and to set a viewing.']

posting_body: ['Hello, thank you for clicking on our craigslist post!', 'Welcome home to Evergreen Townhouse Apartments!', 'These beautiful apartments have a', 'private entrance and a patio.', 'Here you will enjoy plenty of room in an eat-in kitchen and so much cabinet space for you AND your leftovers.', 'Not to mention, your new pantry, which is WALK-IN and so spacious, you will have enough food stored for weeks!', "You'll enjoy having company downstairs while your rooms are all set up, upstairs.", 'We provide laundry on site next door to our main office, where you can stop by and say hello to our friendly leasing agents and property manager at any time.', 'Rents start at $1,300.00-$1,500.00 for the 2-bedroom apartments and $1,525.00-$1,700.00 for the 3-bedroom apartments.', 'The rental amount INCLUDES FREE heat, hot water, and gas for cooking.', 'You can cook all you want for the holidays with no worries!', 'The rent ALSO includes trash and snow removal.', 'What can be better?!', 'With these unbeatable prices, we also provide 24/7 emergency maintenance.', 'Have a problem?', 'Call your leasing office and we will send out, our properly trained crew out to your apartment to solve any issues!', "However, these amazing apartments won't last long!", 'Call us, email us or stop by!', 'Walk-ins are ALWAYS welcomed here!', 'Call us right now to schedule an appointment to view!']

title: Academic Rental Westbrook CT
posting_body: ['This is an Academic Rental NOT a Year Round lease.', 'The lease runs from Sept. 2022 thru May 2023.', 'The home is fully furnished and there is no storage for furnishings etc other than clothing.', '*To receive a response Please Include Contact Number With Inquiry *', 'Tenant pays utilities - Wifi, propane heat..', 'Owner pays metered water, lawn and yard maintenance.', 'Charming shoreline beach house available for Academic Rental only (Not available for year round rental).', 'Sept. 2022 thru May/June 2023', 'This lovely home is located just a short 3 minute stroll to the private beach community of Chapman Beach in Westbrook CT (on the Old Saybrook border).', 'This FULLY Furnished (only available as fully furnished) cozy year round beach home has three bedrooms - 2 queen beds, one of which is a memory foam mattress and 1 full sized bed in the other.', 'The M/Bdrm has a large flat screened tv.', 'Mattresses are encased in zippered covers.', 'The living room has a comfy couch, chairs, and a large flat screen t.v.', 'The kitchen is well-equipped with every gadget you could need and a generous assortment of pots, pans and bake ware.', 'Located off the kitchen is a cheery 3 season porch.', 'Comfy furniture make this the perfect spot to curl up with a good book or relax with friends for coffee and conversation.', 'The grassy back yard is spacious and inviting and has a picnic table, outdoor chairs and a gas grill.', 'There is hot and cold running water in the spacious outside shower.', 'The neighborhood is perfect for leisurely afternoon walks and bike riding.', 'A long stretch of private sandy beach is just a short 3 minute stroll away.', 'Easy access to I-95 and Rte 9, Westbrook and Old Saybrook Train Stations', 'Saybrook Center Boutiques and "The Kate", Boston Post Road shops and a variety of Ethnic Restaurants, Westbook and Clinton Shopping Outlets and The Casinos', "Watch Hill, Rhode Island and it's infamous oldest running Carousel are just a 45 minute drive away.", 'The area is quiet and calming yet quickly accessible to many restaurants and entertainment.', 'No Pets', 'No Smoking, Vaping Etc.', '* TO RECEIVE A REPLY PLEASE INCLUDE A CONTACT NUMBER WITH YOUR INQUIRY.', 'REVIEWS BELOW:', 'A peaceful, charming beach cottage with the beauty of the beach year round!', 'This beach house is located in a family friendly neighborhood.', 'The home is clean, updated and move in ready.', 'A large backyard and a stone’s throw from the beach, Chapman Beach has it all.', 'K. Academic Renter', 'Stay Aug.1 thru 31, 2020', 'This 3-bedroom cottage is adorable and roomy.', 'The furnishings are perfect for a cottage and the decorations are beach themed.', 'The kitchen is well-equipped, and the beds are extremely comfortable.', 'It is well-ventilated with many windows to catch the sea breeze.', 'Each room has a ceiling fan which will also keep you comfortable and cool.', 'There is outdoor seating in both the front and back yards and an inviting enclosed porch which is perfect for a rainy day.', 'There are many free movies available on the T.V. and, of course, there is Wi-Fi.', 'Although, quite honestly, this is the perfect cottage to unplug and totally relax.', 'There are so many beach communities nearby where you can just walk or bike to from the cottage and enjoy the views of the sound.', 'My family enjoyed our one-month stay, especially as the cottage is such a short walk to beach.', 'Pat G. and family']

title: Large 1/2 Duplex for Rent!
posting_body: ['- Large 1/2 duplex for rent in Manchester, CT!', '- This unit features 3 large bedrooms, each with their own large closets!', '- Brand-new hardwood floors and fresh paint!', '- There are also 1 1/2 bathrooms, with a full bathroom on the 2nd floor and another 1/2 bath on first floor.', '- The first floor has tons of living space with two large living rooms and an eat-in kitchen!', '- The kitchen is large and open with a stove, refrigerator, dishwasher, garbage disposal, and plenty of cabinet space!', '- There are washer and dryer hookups in the basement, along with plenty of storage space!', '- In addition to multiple closets, there is a huge basement and large attic for all your storage needs.', "- There is also a spacious backyard with room for a children's play area or other activities while also having the privacy of a fence between you and Charter Oak Park.", '- Charter Oak Park has great opportunities for year round activities with basketball, soccer, ice hockey, hiking trails, and a large playground!', '- This unit is located in the desirable Martin School district- perfect for kids!', '-Right around the corner on Main Street, you can find restaurants, bakeries, stores, CVS, bus lines, and countless other activities.', '-The front of the house features a small front porch- the perfect sitting area to relax!', '- There is off-street parking available for up to three cars.', '- The rent is $1950 a month and the tenant is responsible for their own utilities.', '- Security deposit is required.', '- If interested, please call Brian at', 'show contact info', 'and come see it today!']

title: 2 or 3 Bedroom West Hartford Apt. Close to Center & Blue Back Square
posting_body: ['Available September 15th, is this very spacious 2nd floor apartment of a multi-family home in a fantastic West Hartford neighborhood.', 'Right down the street from Morley Elementary (in the KP/Hall High school district), less than a mile to the one-of-a-kind West Hartford Center and even closer to Whole Foods and the restaurants, shops and theatre at Blue Back Square.', 'This large, sunny, living space has an updated kitchen and bathroom, new gas furnace and replacement windows.', ' It features beautiful hardwood floors, french doors, a large dining room, a large living room with a fireplace and an attached sunroom.', ' The kitchen has a large pantry and room for a small table and chairs.', ' The apartment has its own washer and dryer hookups in the basement.', ' One bathroom and a maximum of two parking spots are included with the apartment.', 'There are 3 full-sized bedrooms in this apartment, however, two have been combined (one entrance to both rooms, large archway between the two).', ' These two rooms are ideal as a bedroom with attached home office for working and/or studying from home.', ' They have also been used as a bedroom with attached nursery or sitting/changing room and have exceptionally large closets.', '  The third bedroom also features an extended closet.', 'Landlords live in neighborhood and maintain yard and perform snow removal and any needed repairs promptly.', 'Easy commute to downtown Hartford, UConn Law, UConn Medical, University of Hartford and Trinity.', 'Absolutely no smoking.', 'Friendly dogs considered with nonrefundable deep cleaning pet fee and possibility of slight increase in monthly rent.', '$2,100/mo plus utilities (tenant pays for heat, electricity, etc.).', 'Application, credit check and $2,000 security deposit required.']

title: Cozy is where the heart is and 58Wade is waiting for you
posting_body: ['Cozy is where the heart is and 58 Wade is waiting for you to call it HOME!-', 'show contact info', 'This 3 bedroom 2 full bath home is filled with modern upgrades.', 'The 1st floor has an open concept flowing easily from room to room.', 'The combination living and dining rooms have hard wood floors and easy access to the 2011 remodeled kitchen with all stainless steel appliances and granite countertops.', 'Off the dining room is the family room which could also be used as a first level bedroom with closet space.', 'Upstairs are three bedrooms.', 'The more quaint of the three would be a great baby room or home office.', 'The additional two bedrooms will fit up to a queen.', 'At the end of the hall is the updated bathroom with granite countertops, exhaust and heat fan.', 'Under all carpet are hardwood floors.', 'Back on the 1st floor, you can go to the partially finished basement complete with laundry and a 2nd full bath.', 'Plenty of storage and work space in the basement too.', 'The yard is easy to mow with your private oasis in the back where you can relax on the patio.', '58 Wade is equipped with a whole house generator, updated electrical, replacement windows, fully lined chimney with cap and newer roof.', 'To schedule a showing please call', 'show contact info']

title: Fabulous Duplex with Waterview
posting_body: ['This is a rare opportunity to rent a piece of history.', 'This duplex is part of the famous mansion that once belonged to the founder of the Peter Pan bus line.', "The unit was originally a detached house that the owner had bought from his neighbor to use for his maid's residence.", 'It has two bedrooms, one and a half bathrooms, a kitchen with breakfast nook, a walk-in closet, a dining area and a fabulously large living room.', 'The house has picture windows looking out onto 2 acres of manicured lawn and gardens, and a view of Bass Pond (use of grounds is not part of the rental).', "The property is located in the prestigious Sixteen Acres District, a Springfield suburb that's far from downtown, and just minutes away from high end restaurants, shops, groceries, parks, golf course and country club.", 'First, last, security are required before move-in.', 'Rent includes all utilities.', 'A rental application must be completed before the property can be shown.', 'Send an email inquiry for the application.']

title: New Modern Studio!!! Private Parking&Porch! ALL UTILITIES INCLUDED!!
posting_body: ['Gut renovated cozy studio on the first floor of a beautiful Victorian Home.', 'The house is located right next to a community garden in the historic west end of Hartford.', 'The building is very quiet with respectful young professionals as your neighbors.', ' The apartment has been completely renovated top to bottom with all modern fixtures.', ' Carpet in photos is being replaced as well.', 'It has a private entrance in the back of the bldg steps away from your parking spot and has a private porch which overlooks a beautiful public garden in the warmer months.', 'The private parking spot along with storage space, heat, electricity, and water are all included in the rent!', 'Very convenient location right off of Farmington Avenue within 5 minute walk of bus stop, grocery store, laundromat, pharmacy, bank, FedEx/Kinkos, gas station, many bars & restaurants.', 'Less than 10 minute walk to UConn Law School and within 5 minute drive of University of Hartford.', 'For single tenant only.', 'This is a non-smoking building.', 'No dogs permitted.', 'Verification of employment & references may be required.', "Available for one year lease with first/last plus one month's security deposit due at signing.", 'If interested, please email a little something about yourself and your occupation.', 'I will get back to you shortly & we can schedule a time for you to come take a look!', 'Look forward to hearing from you!', 'Dave']

title: Welcome to your new home!
posting_body: ['Welcome to your new home!', 'A beautiful 3 bedroom 2.5 bath house in ever popular Walek Farms neighborhood in South Manchester, perfect for a couple or a small family.', 'The house sits on top of the hill with beautiful views towards west, and has a private flat backyard overlooking wooded town parcel, where you could go for walks on the trails that are accessible from up the street.', 'This is a lovely, well maintained and family oriented neighborhood close to schools and parks with easy access to highway.', 'This house boasts an open floor plan, newer wood flooring on main floor, a beautifully finished walk out basement, updated bathrooms, 3 nice-sized bedrooms upstairs with a large room size master closet.', 'Professionally finished basement adds 600 sqft and is a great entertainment area that opens to a small patio perfect for sitting in summer and making marsh mellows at night.']

title: Llama hoy para mas informacion!
posting_body: ['¡Hola y bienvenido a casa en Evergreen Townhouse Apartments!', 'Estos hermosos apartamentos tienen una entrada privada y patio.', 'Aquí disfrutará de mucho espacio en una cocina-comedor y mucho espacio de gabinetes para usted y sus sobras.', 'Sin mencionar que su nueva despensa, que es WALK-IN, es tan espaciosa que tendrá suficiente comida almacenada durante semanas.', 'Disfrutará de tener compañía abajo mientras sus habitaciones están configuradas, arriba.', 'Ofrecemos lavandería en el lugar contiguo a nuestra oficina principal, donde puede pasar a saludar a nuestros amigables agentes de arrendamiento y al administrador de la propiedad en cualquier momento.', 'Los alquileres comienzan en $1,300.00- $1,500.00 para los apartamentos de 2 habitaciones y $1,525.00- $1,700.00 para los apartamentos de 3 habitaciones.', 'El monto del alquiler INCLUYE calefacción, agua caliente y gas GRATIS para cocinar.', '¡Puedes cocinar todo lo que quieras para los días festivos sin preocupaciones!', 'El alquiler también incluye la eliminación de basura y nieve.', '¿Qué puede ser mejor?', 'Con estos precios inmejorables, también ofrecemos mantenimiento de emergencia las 24 horas, los 7 días de la semana.', '¿Tienes un problema?', '¡Llama a tu oficina de arrendamiento y enviaremos a nuestro equipo debidamente capacitado a tu apartamento para resolver cualquier problema!', 'Sin embargo, estos increíbles apartamentos no durarán mucho.', '¡Llámenos, envíenos un correo electrónico o pase por aquí!', '¡Los walk-ins SIEMPRE son bienvenidos aquí!', '¡Llámenos ahora para programar una cita para ver!']

title: Cozy is where the heart is and 58Wade is waiting for you
posting_body: ['Cozy is where the heart is and 58 Wade is waiting for you to call it HOME!', 'This 3 bedroom 2 full bath home is filled with modern upgrades.', 'The 1st floor has an open concept flowing easily from room to room.', 'The combination living and dining rooms have hard wood floors and easy access to the 2011 remodeled kitchen with all stainless steel appliances and granite countertops.', 'Off the dining room is the family room which could also be used as a first level bedroom with closet space.', 'Upstairs are three bedrooms.', 'The more quaint of the three would be a great baby room or home office.', 'The additional two bedrooms will fit up to a queen.', 'At the end of the hall is the updated bathroom with granite countertops, exhaust and heat fan.', 'Under all carpet are hardwood floors.', 'Back on the 1st floor, you can go to the partially finished basement complete with laundry and a 2nd full bath.', 'Plenty of storage and work space in the basement too.', 'The yard is easy to mow with your private oasis in the back where you can relax on the patio.', '58 Wade is equipped with a whole house generator, updated electrical, replacement windows, fully lined chimney with cap and newer roof.', 'To know more, Call : 📞📞📞', 'show contact info', '📞📞📞']
